"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_ebay_connector=self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_ebay_connector||[]).push([[215],{569(e,r,o){o.r(r),o.d(r,{comp:()=>d,data:()=>c});var t=o(641);const a=o.p+"assets/img/import-order-from-ebay.2a88f1e2.webp",s=o.p+"assets/img/order-source.616b50fc.webp",n=o.p+"assets/img/auto-order-import-setting.f76961ce.webp",i=o.p+"assets/img/order-import-default-status.2cb70799.webp",m={},d=(0,o(6262).A)(m,[["render",function(e,r){return(0,t.uX)(),(0,t.CE)("div",null,[...r[0]||(r[0]=[(0,t.Fv)('<h1 id="order-management-–-woocommerce-ebay-connector" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#order-management-–-woocommerce-ebay-connector"><span>Order Management – WooCommerce eBay Connector</span></a></h1><p>This guide explains how to import eBay orders into your WooCommerce store.</p><hr><h2 id="import-orders-from-ebay" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#import-orders-from-ebay"><span>Import Orders from eBay</span></a></h2><p>The admin can import orders from the eBay store to the WooCommerce store.</p><p>Navigate to <strong>WC eBay Connector → Manage Orders</strong> to see the import tab.</p><p><img src="'+a+'" alt="screenshots"></p><h3 id="steps-to-import-orders" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#steps-to-import-orders"><span>Steps to Import Orders</span></a></h3><ol><li>Click <strong>Import Orders from eBay</strong>.</li><li>Select <strong>Start Time From</strong> and <strong>Start Time To</strong> to define the date range.</li><li>Click the <strong>Start</strong> button to import the orders.</li></ol><p>The orders will be imported from eBay into your WooCommerce store.</p><hr><h2 id="order-source-tracking" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#order-source-tracking"><span>Order Source Tracking</span></a></h2><p>The WooCommerce Orders list shows an <strong>Order Source</strong> column to identify if orders come from WooCommerce or eBay, helping admins track orders efficiently.</p><p><img src="'+s+'" alt="screenshots"></p><hr><h2 id="auto-order-import" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#auto-order-import"><span>Auto Order Import</span></a></h2><p>You can configure automatic order import in the plugin settings:</p><ul><li>Navigate to <strong>WC eBay Connector → eBay Settings → General Settings</strong></li><li>Enable <strong>Auto Order Import</strong></li><li>The auto import executes every <strong>10 minutes</strong> and retrieves orders placed within the last <strong>15 minutes</strong></li></ul><p><img src="'+n+'" alt="screenshots"></p><blockquote><p><strong>Note:</strong> All products must be imported for real-time order import to work correctly.</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="order-status" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#order-status"><span>Order Status</span></a></h2><p>You can set the default order status for orders imported from eBay:</p><ul><li>Navigate to <strong>eBay Settings → General Settings</strong></li><li>Set <strong>eBay Imported Order Status</strong> to your preferred default status</li></ul><p><img src="'+i+'" alt="screenshots"></p><hr>',26)])])}]]),c=JSON.parse('{"path":"/documentation/order-management.html","title":"Order Management – WooCommerce eBay Connector","lang":"en-US","frontmatter":{},"git":{"updatedTime":1772114569000,"contributors":[{"name":"shakir.hussain","username":"","email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","commits":1},{"name":"aadesh","username":"","email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","commits":1}],"changelog":[{"hash":"2d5c39163a248635a79c60d8508c0716b0a11c03","time":1772114569000,"email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","author":"aadesh","message":"add export product"},{"hash":"277c5a1bdc13e06551e102ee26c728b6b048e50b","time":1771481506000,"email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","author":"shakir.hussain","message":"updated ebay blog and move to dev"}]},"filePathRelative":"documentation/order-management.md"}')}}]);